{
    "segments": [
        {
            "start": 0.75,
            "end": 3.15,
            "text": "I think we got off on the wrong foot earlier."
        },
        {
            "start": 3.15,
            "end": 5.15,
            "text": "I'm a musician too."
        },
        {
            "start": 5.15,
            "end": 7.15,
            "text": "Writer, not performer."
        },
        {
            "start": 7.15,
            "end": 9.65,
            "text": "You're sick, yeah. What kind of stuff do you have?"
        },
        {
            "start": 9.65,
            "end": 12.65,
            "text": "Uh, classical mostly."
        },
        {
            "start": 12.65,
            "end": 14.65,
            "text": "Yeah, classical."
        },
        {
            "start": 14.65,
            "end": 17.15,
            "text": "But I'm trying out other styles too."
        },
        {
            "start": 17.15,
            "end": 22.65,
            "text": "Like pop, folk, R&B, rock, electronic."
        },
        {
            "start": 22.65,
            "end": 26.15,
            "text": "But mostly pop, though, and classical."
        },
        {
            "start": 26.15,
            "end": 27.65,
            "text": "Well, see?"
        },
        {
            "start": 27.65,
            "end": 29.65,
            "text": "Good."
        },
        {
            "start": 29.65,
            "end": 33.96,
            "text": "Hey, I am always selling you to wear your jacket. You never do."
        },
        {
            "start": 33.96,
            "end": 35.96,
            "text": "Oh, no!"
        },
        {
            "start": 35.96,
            "end": 40.85,
            "text": "Hey, I'm uh..."
        },
        {
            "start": 40.85,
            "end": 43.35,
            "text": "I know you are, man. And you went out at Eastwood today."
        },
        {
            "start": 43.35,
            "end": 45.35,
            "text": "Yeah, thanks man."
        },
        {
            "start": 45.35,
            "end": 47.35,
            "text": "You're a doggie fan?"
        },
        {
            "start": 47.35,
            "end": 49.35,
            "text": "Yeah, my dad played."
        },
        {
            "start": 49.35,
            "end": 51.35,
            "text": "Nothing like Phil Graham."
        },
        {
            "start": 51.35,
            "end": 54.35,
            "text": "But uh, yeah, we'd watch together."
        },
        {
            "start": 54.35,
            "end": 56.35,
            "text": "Yeah."
        },
        {
            "start": 56.35,
            "end": 58.35,
            "text": "You're Hannah, right?"
        },
        {
            "start": 58.35,
            "end": 60.35,
            "text": "Yeah."
        },
        {
            "start": 60.35,
            "end": 65.16,
            "text": "Hannah Wells."
        },
        {
            "start": 65.56,
            "end": 67.56,
            "text": "Now it's nice to meet you."
        },
        {
            "start": 67.56,
            "end": 69.56,
            "text": "Yeah."
        },
        {
            "start": 69.56,
            "end": 72.56,
            "text": "Oh, okay."
        },
        {
            "start": 72.56,
            "end": 74.56,
            "text": "I was out of my mind."
        },
        {
            "start": 74.56,
            "end": 79.64,
            "text": "See you around. Sweet."
        },
        {
            "start": 79.64,
            "end": 81.64,
            "text": "Yeah, how was that? And how'd you suddenly know my name?"
        },
        {
            "start": 81.64,
            "end": 83.64,
            "text": "Don't worry about it. And you're welcome."
        },
        {
            "start": 83.64,
            "end": 85.64,
            "text": "For..."
        },
        {
            "start": 85.64,
            "end": 87.64,
            "text": "Now Jacob knows who you are."
        },
        {
            "start": 87.64,
            "end": 89.64,
            "text": "Justin."
        },
        {
            "start": 89.64,
            "end": 92.64,
            "text": "Whatever. Look, guys like that only want what someone else has."
        },
        {
            "start": 92.64,
            "end": 95.64,
            "text": "Especially when that someone is a briar to you athlete."
        },
        {
            "start": 96.04,
            "end": 99.04,
            "text": "I hear you have a healthy opinion of yourself, don't you?"
        },
        {
            "start": 99.04,
            "end": 101.04,
            "text": "I actually thought that was pretty modest."
        },
        {
            "start": 101.04,
            "end": 103.04,
            "text": "I could have said starting center, team captain,"
        },
        {
            "start": 103.04,
            "end": 108.4,
            "text": "highest score for two seasons straight."
        },
        {
            "start": 108.4,
            "end": 122.72,
            "text": "It worked, didn't it?"
        },
        {
            "start": 122.72,
            "end": 127.57,
            "text": "Why do you care? I haven't been particularly nice to you."
        },
        {
            "start": 127.57,
            "end": 130.95,
            "text": "You're a music major, right?"
        },
        {
            "start": 130.95,
            "end": 132.95,
            "text": "I saw your Instagram."
        },
        {
            "start": 132.95,
            "end": 134.95,
            "text": "You, uh..."
        },
        {
            "start": 134.95,
            "end": 139.95,
            "text": "You sort of disappear when you play."
        },
        {
            "start": 139.95,
            "end": 142.95,
            "text": "I don't mean that in a bad way."
        },
        {
            "start": 143.35,
            "end": 145.35,
            "text": "You love it, I can tell."
        },
        {
            "start": 145.35,
            "end": 149.01,
            "text": "You love hockey like that?"
        },
        {
            "start": 149.01,
            "end": 159.76,
            "text": "It's just something I've always done to impress my dad."
        },
        {
            "start": 159.76,
            "end": 163.46,
            "text": "And does it?"
        },
        {
            "start": 163.46,
            "end": 165.46,
            "text": "Nothing impresses him."
        },
        {
            "start": 165.46,
            "end": 167.46,
            "text": "Not really."
        },
        {
            "start": 167.46,
            "end": 174.29,
            "text": "What about your mom?"
        },
        {
            "start": 174.29,
            "end": 179.62,
            "text": "She, um... she died."
        },
        {
            "start": 179.62,
            "end": 193.64,
            "text": "Look, I don't believe in favors or shortcuts."
        },
        {
            "start": 193.64,
            "end": 196.64,
            "text": "I don't want to pass this class because somebody handed me the grade."
        },
        {
            "start": 196.64,
            "end": 200.62,
            "text": "I want to earn it."
        },
        {
            "start": 200.62,
            "end": 203.62,
            "text": "I'm pretty sure you're the only one who can help me do that."
        },
        {
            "start": 203.62,
            "end": 205.62,
            "text": "It was so what?"
        },
        {
            "start": 205.62,
            "end": 207.62,
            "text": "I helped you study for the midterm"
        },
        {
            "start": 207.62,
            "end": 210.62,
            "text": "and you played my fake boyfriend to get Justin's attention?"
        },
        {
            "start": 210.62,
            "end": 214.09,
            "text": "Something like that?"
        },
        {
            "start": 214.09,
            "end": 217.09,
            "text": "I had to self-depay me."
        },
        {
            "start": 217.09,
            "end": 229.24,
            "text": "Obviously."
        },
        {
            "start": 229.24,
            "end": 231.24,
            "text": "Don't forget."
        },
        {
            "start": 231.24,
            "end": 233.24,
            "text": "I'm not your girl, Graham."
        },
        {
            "start": 234.24,
            "end": 237.24,
            "text": "This is my dance space. This is your dance space."
        },
        {
            "start": 237.24,
            "end": 239.24,
            "text": "I don't go into years. You don't come into mine."
        },
        {
            "start": 239.24,
            "end": 241.24,
            "text": "You've seen dirty dancing."
        },
        {
            "start": 241.24,
            "end": 243.24,
            "text": "That's my mom's favorite movie."
        },
        {
            "start": 243.24,
            "end": 247.54,
            "text": "Still a dated reference, though."
        },
        {
            "start": 247.54,
            "end": 249.54,
            "text": "So messy."
        },
        {
            "start": 249.54,
            "end": 251.54,
            "text": "Hey, this is why this is perfect."
        },
        {
            "start": 251.54,
            "end": 255.54,
            "text": "You're not interested in me and I'm not interested in a relationship."
        },
        {
            "start": 255.54,
            "end": 258.54,
            "text": "So this arrangement is mutually beneficial?"
        },
        {
            "start": 258.54,
            "end": 260.54,
            "text": "Purely transactional."
        },
        {
            "start": 260.54,
            "end": 264.62,
            "text": "So?"
        }
    ],
    "summary": {
        "overview": "Hannah and Graham discuss their backgrounds in music and sports, sharing personal insights and motivations while establishing a partnership to support each other's goals.",
        "discussion_points": [
